      <h2 class="section-heading">You already have the agents. Now orchestrate them.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Coding agents are powerful &mdash; but running them manually, one issue at a time, doesn't scale. Itervox turns them into a fleet.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="compare-grid">
