        <div class="compare-title">Manual Claude Code / Codex</div>
        <ol class="compare-steps">
          <li><span><span class="compare-step-num">1.</span> Open terminal, pick an issue</span> <span class="compare-step-time">manual</span></li>
          <li><span><span class="compare-step-num">2.</span> Create branch, cd into repo</span> <span class="compare-step-time">manual</span></li>
          <li><span><span class="compare-step-num">3.</span> Run <code style="font-size:11px;background:var(--bg-elevated);padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;">claude</code> with a prompt</span> <span class="compare-step-time">manual</span></li>
          <li><span><span class="compare-step-num">4.</span> Wait for agent to finish</span> <span class="compare-step-time">blocked</span></li>
          <li><span><span class="compare-step-num">5.</span> Review output, create PR</span> <span class="compare-step-time">manual</span></li>
          <li><span><span class="compare-step-num">6.</span> Repeat for next issue</span> <span class="compare-step-time">serial</span></li>
