      </div>
      <div class="int-card">
        <div class="int-icon" style="color: var(--danger);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="7"/><line x1="9" y1="5" x2="9" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Stall Detection</h4>
        <p>If an agent produces no output within the stall timeout (default 5 min), the worker is killed and the issue is retried automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="int-card">
        <div class="int-icon" style="color: var(--teal);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="7"/><path d="M7 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Auto-Pause on Open PR</h4>
