      </div>
      <div class="int-card">
        <div class="int-icon" style="color: var(--success);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="7" width="12" height="8" rx="2"/><path d="M6 7V5a3 3 0 0 1 6 0v2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>API Authentication</h4>
        <p>Set <code style="font-size:10px; background:var(--bg-elevated); padding:0 3px; border-radius:2px;">ITERVOX_API_TOKEN</code> to enable Bearer token auth on all API routes. Essential for production deployments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- YOLO mode callout -->
